<br>
I don't view any of this as jumping on anyone for being a casual player.  I myself am a casual player.  I work 2 jobs, play EQ a few nights a week for about 2-3 hrs, and play every other weekend, sometimes for long stretches, sometimes little to none, depending on what I have brewing IRL.<br>
<br>
Yet, with that said, yes I am jumping down people's throats (kinda) for the complaining, because it has grown so much, and it gets very tiring.<br>
<br>
I don't judge anyone for being a casual player.  What is most irritating is that they can't accept that they are casual players, and that the players who are NOT casual will naturally progress further.  It is NOT Verant's fault that anyone is a casual player.  Basically, I agree with what the guy said above.  People should accept what is given in this game (which is aimed at team work, and long playtime), or go find another hobby.  Sitting around griping doesn't fix anything, but instead it makes things less enjoyable for those who DO accept where they stand.  There are tons of games, and loads of other things one could do with their leisure time. <p><table><tr><td><img src=http://home.sc.rr.com/kimmisc/defEnvy2.gif></td><td><img src=http://home.sc.rr.com/kimmisc/big_t.gif border="0"><img src=http://home.sc.rr.com/kimmisc/small_e.gif border="0"><img src=http://home.sc.rr.com/kimmisc/small_l.gif border="0"><img src=http://home.sc.rr.com/kimmisc/small_d.gif border="0"><img src=http://home.sc.rr.com/kimmisc/small_i.gif border="0"><img src=http://home.sc.rr.com/kimmisc/small_v.gif border="0"><img src=http://home.sc.rr.com/kimmisc/small_a.gif border="0"><img src=http://home.sc.rr.com/kimmisc/big_g.gif border="0"><img src=http://home.sc.rr.com/kimmisc/small_r.gif border="0"><img src=http://home.sc.rr.com/kimmisc/small_i.gif border="0"><img src=http://home.sc.rr.com/kimmisc/small_m.gif border="0"><img src=http://home.sc.rr.com/kimmisc/apostrophy.gif border="0"><img src=http://home.sc.rr.com/kimmisc/big_l.gif border="0"><img src=http://home.sc.rr.com/kimmisc/small_e.gif border="0"><img src=http://home.sc.rr.com/kimmisc/small_u.gif border="0"><img src=http://home.sc.rr.com/kimmisc/small_x.gif border="0"></a><BR><b><font color="#049430"><font size="2" face="Times New Roman"><i>55 Conjurer - Officer of The Claw of Nagafen<BR>Just cloak, embers, Hate staff, and crown away from epic enabledness!<BR>Bristlebane<BR><a href=mailto:teldiva@hotmail.com>Email</a> -- <a href=http://eq